Personal Data we collect about you. We will use this Personal Data:

        to administer our Website or app and for internal operations, including troubleshooting, data analysis, testing, research, statistical and survey purposes;
        to improve our Products and to ensure that Website or app content is presented in the most effective manner for you and for your computer or device;
        to allow you to participate in interactive features of our Website or app and services, when you choose to do so;
        as part of our efforts to keep our Website or app safe and secure;
        to make suggestions and recommendations to you and other users of our Website or app about goods or services that may interest you or them;
        to send you an email if you have bought from us either in store or online, inviting you to review the product/s bought.  You will be able to unsubscribe from these emails;
        to make suggestions and recommendations to you based on purchases you have made whilst providing your personal data, Hobbycraft loyalty card number, or a credit or debit card.

